              "display_title": "Kohrak-Kal",
              "description": "Kohrak-Kal often works alone - its sonic powers are so great, they are even a threat to the other Bohrok-Kal! In fact, the Kohrak-Kal’s power is so awesome that its Krana can afford to ignore danger until the very last moment. When the Kohrak-Kal finally reacts to a threat, it does so swiftly and with overpowering effect.",
